mirror cmdr: wrong#args, not enough

mail reply add [OPTIONS] <reply> <text>
    Add a new reply template. By default the template will not cause mail to be sent.

    --auto-mail         Automatically send mail when this reply is used.
    --color             Force the (non-)use of colors in the output. The default depends on the environment, active when talking to a tty, and otherwise not.
    --database DATABASE Use an alternate database instead of the default.
    --no-color          Complementary alias of --color.
    --verbose           Activate more chatter.
    -D DATABASE         Alias of --database.
    -M                  Alias of --auto-mail.
    -v                  Alias of --verbose.

    reply The name for a not-yet-known reply template.
    text  The text of the template
